{
  "stem": "4830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The so-called Jewish laws came in, three of them, and while the first one was rather innocent, the main objection to Jews was that Jews occupy important economic positions and many important positions much higher than that percentage.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the first Jewish law regulated that Jews cannot be any more in percentage in any given place than 20%.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the second one reduced it to 5%.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The 20% was basically-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I'm not sure where they got this 20% percent, but this approached more the number of Jews that were approximately 600,000 in Hungary, which was about 15% of the population.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish boys were out, and I did not join the Boy Scout movement again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not for any reason that I wanted to demonstrate anything, but I got interested in other things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So my Boy Scout career ended at age 9 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have memories of Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very strict in those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went, of course, to the synagogue on each and every occasion when there was a chance to go, because my father took us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had some pertinent questions fairly early.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just, for example, to give you one-- I don't know exactly how old I was, I was around 10, 11-- when my father woke me up at 6 o'clock in the morning that we have to go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The orthodox service started at 6:30.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I told him that I'm very sleepy, maybe I could go later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, this is not a good idea because I have to go because today we are praying for our life-- that we will be in the Book of Life for the next year.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
